defaultIt is difficult to believe that the assessors are able to investigate 8x more cases with no additional resources.
default&#xa0;
default Many of these cases are extremely complex.
default&#xa0;
default It is our strong suspicion that ‘assessments’ are now termed ‘investigations’ in order to meet this target with very little change in the process.
